30</td><td>-3.28</td></tr><tr><td>百濟神州(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06160:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06160\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06160-HK</a>)</td><td>159.60</td><td>-3.21</td></tr><tr><td>康方生物(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09926:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09926\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09926-HK</a>)</td><td>85.30</td><td>-3.07</td></tr><tr><td>榮昌生物(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09995:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09995\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09995-HK</a>)</td><td>27.30</td><td>+1.87</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　(ed)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
